## Component Guidelines
1. Use theme-aware components for consistent theming
2. Follow the component directory structure
3. Implement proper TypeScript types
4. Use proper prop types and default values
5. Include proper documentation

## Icon Usage
Icons are managed through the `IconSymbol` component:
```typescript
import { IconSymbol } from '@/components/ui/IconSymbol';

// Usage
<IconSymbol name="game-controller" size={24} />
```

